    <intervention_name>HPN-100</intervention_name>
    <description>HPN-100 will be administered orally three times daily (TID) with meals. The maximum recommended dose of HPN-100 in subjects weighing less than 20 kg is 0.53 mL/kg/day (equivalent to 600 mg/kg/day of NaPBA), and is 11.48 mL/m2/day in heavier subjects (equivalent to 13g/m2/day of NaPBA). The maximum HPN-100 dose should be 17.4 mL/day, which is equivalent to 20 g/day of NaPBA.</description>
