  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male and female subjects who completed HPN-100-005,(NCT00947544),
             HPN-100-007,(NCT00947297), or HPN-100-012,(NCT01347073).

          -  Signed informed consent by subject and/or subject's legally authorized
             representative.

          -  Negative pregnancy test for all females of childbearing potential.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any clinical or laboratory abnormality or medical condition that, at the discretion
             of the investigator, may put the subject at increased risk when participating.

          -  Known hypersensitivity to PAA,(phenylacetate) or PBA,(phenylbutyrate).

          -  Liver transplant, including hepatocellular transplant.

          -  Pregnant, breastfeeding or lactating females.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
